constant fraction of\nthe optimal revenue in a very weak correlation, this method alone can not\ndirectly show the efficiency of the mechanism in stronger correlations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Dec 2014 02:52:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2015 13:02:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-23"}
